events.name: Learning City: Where Craft Meets Technology
events.description: Join Science Centre Singapore and Community Partners GUILD - Ground-Up Innovation Labs for Development Repair Kopitiam HackerspaceSG Kee Wee Teng Anjali Venkat Priyanka Gupta Sarvaiya Elda Webb Engineering Good The Tinkering Studio Come and Make Imagin8ors to try hands onactivitities like water rockets, marble machines, kite making, Virtual reality, glass mosaics, paper quilling, laser cutting and more. Lets celebrate the Maker mindset at the Istana this labor day! This programme is supported by the Learn SG
